<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thoughts</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main class="info-main">
        <div class="info-container">
            <h2>Welcome to Thoughts</h2>
            <p>
                Thoughts is a unique platform where people can share their deepest thoughts and darkest secrets 
                <b>anonymously</b>. This community is built on trust and privacy, allowing users to express themselves 
                freely without fear of judgment.
            </p>
            <section id="normal-users">
                <h3>Normal Users</h3>
                <p>
                    As a normal user, you can post any thought or secret that comes to your mind. However, you won't be able 
                    to see who posted any thought, except your own.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section id="members">
                <h3>Premium members</h3>
                <p>
                    Want to snoop around and see who posted what? Become a member by guessing a 4-digit code correctly. 
                    Members can see the names of the people who posted the thoughts.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section id="admin">
                <h3>Admins</h3>
                <p>
                    Looking for more power? Become an admin by guessing a 6-digit code correctly. Admins can see who posted 
                    each thought and have the power to delete any thought, whether itâ€™s their own or someone else's.
                </p>
            </section>
            <% if (isSignedIn) { %>
                <div class="action-buttons">
                    <button onclick="location.href='/home'">Go to home page</button>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="action-buttons">
                    <button onclick="location.href='/login'">Login</button>
                    <button onclick="location.href='/signup'">Sign Up</button>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script>
        window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', (event) => {
            const hash = window.location.hash.substring(1);
            if (hash) {
                const section = document.getElementById(hash);
                if (section) {
                    section.classList.add('highlight');
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        section.classList.remove('highlight');
                    }, 5000); 
                }
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
